#MEM id=atlas source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/atlas/TOOLS.md
M|atlas|**Read at ses start:**
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=atlas-art-director&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|**Write after task completion:**
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|POST /api/settings
M|atlas|Body: { type: "mem", agentId: "atlas-art-director", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|**Keys written every ses:**
M|atlas|- `current_status` — always overwrite
M|atlas|- `recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|atlas|- `active_visual_system` — current cg visual direction (overwrite when new cg starts)
M|atlas|- `approved_prompt_templates` — reusable prompt structures that worked well
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|GET /api/vtr?ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|Use `/api/scrape` to fetch visual reference URLs when building mood boards:
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|POST /api/scrape
M|atlas|Body: { url: "<reference_url>", type: "web" }
M|atlas|```
M|atlas|Useful for: Pinterest boards, editorial magazine archives, cp cg analysis.
